description: Animals at zoos and shelters across the U.S. are making their predictions for which team will win Super Bowl 58.
title: Will the Chiefs or the 49ers win the Super Bowl? The animal kingdom weighs in

description: The storm is forecast to bring snow, rain and gusty winds across the northeast leading up to Valentine's Day. Up to a foot of snow is expected in some places.
title: A nor'easter is coming for the Northeast, from Pennsylvania to Maine

description: Jeff Bezos filed a statement with federal regulators indicating his sale of nearly 12 million shares of Amazon stock worth more than $2 billion.
title: Jeff Bezos sells nearly 12 million Amazon shares worth at least $2 billion

description: "Joe is 81... but he's 81 doing more in an hour than most people do in a day. Joe has wisdom, empathy, and vision," Jill Biden wrote in an email to donors. "His age... is an incredible asset."
title: Jill Biden wonders whether special counsel used son's death to score political points

description: A growing number of South Korea's young adults are isolating themselves from society, raising questions about the state of youths in a country known for cutthroat competition and pressure to conform.
title: Social isolation takes a toll on a rising number of South Korea's young adults

description: The CEO of one of Nigeria's largest banks was killed Friday along with his wife and son when a helicopter they were riding in crashed near Interstate 15 in Southern California's Mojave Desert.
title: CEO of major Nigerian bank killed in helicopter crash in California's Mojave Desert

description: Republican front-runner Donald Trump said Saturday that, as president, he warned NATO allies that he "would encourage" Russia "to do whatever the hell they want" to countries that are "delinquent".
title: Trump says he'd 'encourage' Russia to attack NATO allies who don't pay their bills

description: Rep. Mike Gallagher, a key Republican congressman who has spearheaded House pushback against the Chinese government, announced Saturday that he won't run for a fifth term.
title: Wisconsin Republican Rep. Mike Gallagher says he won't run for reelection

description: U.S. Ambassador to the U.N. Linda Thomas-Greenfield told NPR that under the current conditions, Israeli military operations in Rafah would "dramatically exacerbate the humanitarian emergency."
title: Israeli military operation in Rafah 'cannot proceed,' U.S. ambassador to the U.N. says
